snippet.title: The Omaga Project
snippet.description:
Social & political satirical commentary videos that include some of the following topics:


🔴


*Identity Politics
*Traditional Politics
*Mainstream media and their lies.


🔴


Whether that is trashing the modern product and their Wokeness or with Fan Boy excitement (which usually gets crushed with Identity Politics) I'm a big nerd at heart and you'll get some of that too.


🔴


DISCLAIMER: These are the ramblings of some idiot for entertainment purposes only and are all factually inaccurate and disinformation based in an attempt to parody the crazy nuts who believe this stuff.

Please ignore me!


🔴


*Famous Quote:
"Two weeks to stop the spread"
- Some person on full pay all year 🙄🙄🙄


🔴


Just to be clear Liberals, I do not dislike anyone based on their Gender, Skin Colour, Sexual Preferences, or their Identity. It also means that a person does not get special treatment. Everyone is treated the same, regardless of "Identity". 


🔴


#MAGA2020


🔴


Thank you
